<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-large-font-size">Who we are</h2>



<p>Established in 2008, dxw is a diverse multidisciplinary team of digital strategy, design, technology and delivery specialists.</p>



<p>We work in partnership with our clients to make life better for the people who use public services and the teams that run them.</p>



<p>In 2021, the company became <a href="/employee-owned/">employee owned</a>. We committed ourselves to working in the best interests of public service users, and our staff, as part of our trust deeds.</p>



<p>In January this year, <a href="/neontribe-joins-the-dxw-family/">Neontribe joined the dxw family</a>. Specialists in supporting the third sector, we’re working together to expand our offer and deliver our mission to improve lives.</p>
